{"article_id":"cXH3GGAtt5LmDAPF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New York state has enacted strong new legal protections for abortion rights .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"The new law ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"signed by Governor Andrew Cuomo on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"safeguards rights","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"laid out in Roe v. Wade and other court rulings ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"including a provision","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"permitting late-term abortions","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"when a woman 's health is endangered ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The Associated Press reports .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"The state 's previous law ,","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"which had been on the books for nearly 50 years ,","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"only permitted abortions after 24 weeks of pregnancy","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"if a woman 's life was at risk .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"Governor Cuomo celebrated the passing of the bill in the Democrat-led Senate and Assembly on Tuesday ,","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"which happened to be the 46th anniversary of the Roe decision .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"`` In the face of a federal government intent","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"on rolling back Roe v. Wade and women 's reproductive rights ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"I promised","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that we would enact this critical legislation within the first 30 days of the new session","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"- and we got it done , ''","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Cuomo said in a statement .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"He directed state landmarks like the spire of One World Trade Center to be lit up in pink","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"to `` shine a bright light forward","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"for the rest of the nation","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to follow . ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"`` We 're saying","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"here in New York , women 's lives matter .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"We 're saying","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"here in New York , women 's decisions matter , ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Andrea Stewart-Cousins said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Sarah Weddington , the Texas attorney","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"who successfully argued Roe before Supreme Court ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"was at Cuomo 's side","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"when he signed the Reproductive Health Act into law .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` Thank you for what you 've done for women , ''","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Weddington told the governor , lawmakers and advocates .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The Reproductive Health Act replaces a 1970 state abortion law","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that was passed","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"three years before Roe legalized abortion nationwide .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The new law moves the section of state law","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"dealing with abortion","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"from the penal code to health statutes .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"It also authorizes midwives and physician assistants to perform some abortions ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"CBS New York reports .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Abortion rights supporters pushed for years to update the law .","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"When Democrats gained control of the state Senate this year ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"the act became easier to pass in both chambers .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Supporters said","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"the election of President Donald Trump and the nomination of conservative justices helped galvanize efforts","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to pass this law .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Republicans","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"who opposed the bill","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"offered proposals","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"to create new legal penalties","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"for harming pregnant women .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Some critics argued","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"the bill could make it harder for prosecutors to bring charges","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"when a woman is assaulted and loses her pregnancy ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"the AP reports ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"although Democrats disputed that .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Some opponents also predicted","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"the bill will lead to more late-term abortions .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"According to the New York State Department of Health ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"285,127 induced abortions occurred in the state between 2012 and 2014 .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"The average number of live births for the same three years was 237,499 .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Nationwide , the vast majority of abortions take place in the first trimester .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"The AP reports","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"nine other states","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"including California , Washington and Oregon","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"have also put protections for abortion rights in their state statutes ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"to preserve legal access in those states","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"if Roe is overturned .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":143,"left":84,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":80,"right":83,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":73,"right":77,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":74,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":5,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":81,"righ